high_descs: Cross the room to the dishwasher and face the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife on the counter between the apple and the coffee maker.
Turn left, move to in front of the tomato, turn right and face the tomato.
Use the knife to slice the tomato.
Turn right, move to the sink, turn left, face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn left, move to the tomato slices, turn right to face the tomato slices.
Pick up a tomato slice.
Turn right, move to the sink, turn left, face the sink.
Put the tomato slice in the sink , rinse it off, retrieve the tomato slice.
Cross the room to the table.
Place the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, place a tomato slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and begin walking to the kitchen counter, then hang a left and walk around the island up to where the coffee machine is on the counter.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle that is just to the left of the coffee machine.
Turn left and walk over to the area to the left of the sink.
Use the knife to slice up the tomato that is on the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the sink basin.
Place the large knife inside the sink basin point down.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up a piece of sliced tomato.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the sink basin.
Place the piece of sliced tomato into the sink basin, then turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the now clean piece of sliced tomato.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn right again and walk over to the side of the round wooden table that is closest to the corner of the room.
Place the clean piece of sliced tomato onto the table just below the closest book that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean piece of sliced tomato on the round table.

high_descs: Go to the counter above the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife next to the coffee maker on the counter.
Go past the sink to the counter next to it.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Move over to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Move back to the counter on the left of the sink.
Pick up a tomato slice on the counter.
Move back to the sink.
Rinse the tomato slice in the sink.
Take the cleaned tomato slice to the table.
Set the clean slice of tomato down next to the book on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of tomato on the table.
